Use Case: Login
Scope: BattleShip
Primary Actor: User
Intention: Login to game server with username and password.
Level: User-goal
Multiplicity: Many Users can login at the same time.
Main Success Scenario: 
  1. System displays login form to User
  2. User submits username and password to System
  3. System verifies login information.
  4. System does MatchUser
Extensions: 
  2a. System determines login information is incorrect
      Use case continues at step 1.
